# SuperUI

When a task involves frontend UI work, read and follow:

```text
skills/superui/SKILL.md
```

Start from the `superui` router instead of directly editing UI code. Determine `<ARTIFACT_ROOT>`, read user preferences, then route to the relevant child skill.
